94EL2xfv#?secret=XHQNzaHatQ" data-secret="XHQNzaHatQ" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="EHSKSR3wCb"> <a href="https://p2y.jp/vtuber-oura-rukako-streaming-was-hit-slanderous-comments-such-as-774inc-nanashiinku-is-a-noob-and-it-would-be-hilarious-if-they-were-absorbed-by-nijisanji-etc/">VTuber 大浦るかこの配信に「ななしいんくは無能」「にじさんじに吸収されれば面白い」等の誹謗中傷コメントか</a></blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="&#8220;VTuber 大浦るかこの配信に「ななしいんくは無能」「にじさんじに吸収されれば面白い」等の誹謗中傷コメントか&#8221; &#8212; P2y.jp" src="https://p2y.jp/vtuber-oura-rukako-streaming-was-hit-slanderous-comments-such-as-774inc-nanashiinku-is-a-noob-and-it-would-be-hilarious-if-they-were-absorbed-by-nijisanji-etc/embed/#?secret=IsnDn3ORLh#?secret=EHSKSR3wCb" data-secret="EHSKSR3wCb" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><p></p><blockquote class="wp-block-quote"><p> <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@May_Oinomori" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">May Channel / 狼森メイ 【ななしいんく】</a> ／<a href="https://twitter.com/May_Oinomori" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">狼森メイ<img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f608.png" alt="😈" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/14.0.0/72x72/1f43a.png" alt="🐺" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> @ななしいんく</a>／ <a href="https://www.774.ai/talent/may-oinomori" target="_blank" rel="noopener" title="May Oinomori">May Oinomori</a></p> <cite>YouTube / Twitter / ななしいんく</cite></blockquote><p>( <em>P2y.jp 管理代表者「2号さん (仮)」</em> ／バーチャル・メタバース・VTuber情報)</p><p></p><p></p> The post <a href="https://p2y.jp/nanashiinku-774in